%p Great news! #{@user.name} (cc'd) is now a key member.

%p
  #{@user.name}, to finalize your key membership you must attend a Key Member Orientation. 
  %br/
  At the orientation we will:

%ul 
  %li Set you up with a keycode
  %li Show you how to access and lock up the space
  %li Add you to the key member email list and Google Drive folder
  %li Review the responsibilities of being a key member

%p 
  If there are no key member orientations currently scheduled, the Membership Coordinators will schedule one or you can ask them to meet with you individually (reply-all!). You may optionally attend key member orientation over video chat.

%p
